  <name>ColorSmith</name>
  <summary>A modern color management application</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
      ColorSmith is a simple and elegant application for picking and managing colors.
      It provides an intuitive interface to select colors from your screen, convert between
      color formats (HEX, RGB), and copy color values to your clipboard.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Pick colors from anywhere on your screen using screen picker</li>
      <li>Adjust RGB values with sliders and spin boxes</li>
      <li>Convert between HEX and RGB color formats</li>
      <li>Generate random colors for inspiration</li>
      <li>Copy color values to clipboard with one click</li>
      <li>Remember your last used color</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

